11#ifndef LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_RTP_PACKET_INCOMING_H_
12#define LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_RTP_PACKET_INCOMING_H_
13
14#include <cstddef>
15#include <cstdint>
16#include <memory>
17#include <utility>
18
19#include "api/array_view.h"
20#include "api/rtc_event_log/rtc_event.h"
21#include "modules/rtp_rtcp/source/rtp_packet.h"
22
23namespace webrtc {
24
25class RtpPacketReceived;
26
27class RtcEventRtpPacketIncoming final : public RtcEvent {
28 public:
29 static constexpr Type kType = Type::RtpPacketIncoming;
30
31 explicit RtcEventRtpPacketIncoming(const RtpPacketReceived& packet);
32 ~RtcEventRtpPacketIncoming() override;
33
34 Type GetType() const override { return kType; }
35 bool IsConfigEvent() const override { return false; }
36
37 std::unique_ptr<RtcEventRtpPacketIncoming> Copy() const;
38
39 size_t packet_length() const { return packet_.size(); }
40
41 rtc::ArrayView<const uint8_t> RawHeader() const {
42 return rtc::MakeArrayView(packet_.data(), header_length());
43 }
44 uint32_t Ssrc() const { return packet_.Ssrc(); }
45 uint32_t Timestamp() const { return packet_.Timestamp(); }
46 uint16_t SequenceNumber() const { return packet_.SequenceNumber(); }
47 uint8_t PayloadType() const { return packet_.PayloadType(); }
48 bool Marker() const { return packet_.Marker(); }
49 template <typename ExtensionTrait, typename... Args>
50 bool GetExtension(Args&&... args) const {
51 return packet_.GetExtension<ExtensionTrait>(std::forward<Args>(args)...);
52 }
53 template <typename ExtensionTrait>
54 bool HasExtension() const {
55 return packet_.HasExtension<ExtensionTrait>();
56 }
57
58 size_t payload_length() const { return packet_.payload_size(); }
59 size_t header_length() const { return packet_.headers_size(); }
60 size_t padding_length() const { return packet_.padding_size(); }
61
62 private:
63 RtcEventRtpPacketIncoming(const RtcEventRtpPacketIncoming& other);
64
65 const RtpPacket packet_;
66};
67
68} // namespace webrtc
69
70#endif // LOGGING_RTC_EVENT_LOG_EVENTS_RTC_EVENT_RTP_PACKET_INCOMING_H_
